      <article>
        <p>
          FD9 Group is an environment that brings fashion enthusiasts together to conceptualize, incubate and execute the yet undiscovered creative ideas and business strategies within the fashion Industry.  FD9 Group’s mission is to utilize its creative talent and fashion industry resources to create and develop startup brands and platforms in the fashion space that provide consumers with unique products and services that cannot be found elsewhere.  
        </p>
        <h2>Creative Approach</h2>
        <p>FD9 group evaluates its projects by identifying new niche areas that are not yet serviced or provided for.  With a young and dynamic team, FD9 approaches each project from an imaginative mindset and unique messaging perspective.  Through creative conceptualization, development and execution, a FD9 brand or platform is born.</p>
        <div class="img-placeholder"></div>
          <h2>Manufacturing & Supply Chain</h2>
          <p>A seamless supply chain is very crucial to the success of any company in the fast paced fashion Industry. The modern consumer has more choices and is more demanding than ever before and we strive to meet these market changes.  Through domestic and global partners, FD9 Group has created manufacturing and supply-chain processes to develop products in fast-fashion format that meet the customers demand.</p>

          <h2>Distribution Channels</h2>
          <p>There are more than a fair share of sales channels available to the consumer and with FD9 Group’s brands we have the knowledge and experience to place our brands into the appropriate channels.  With heavy experience and connections in offline sales, and the right partners for online commerce, there is no shortage of expertise at the hands of FD9 Group.</p> 
